\c 20
\s Kurangwa kwezvivi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 2 Utizve kuvana vaIsraeri\x + 18.2.\x*: Ani nani pavana vaIsraeri kana pavatorwa vagere pakati paIsraeri sevaeni anopa \add vamwe\add* vevana vake kuna Moreki, zvirokwazvo achaurawa; vanhu venyika vachamutaka nemabwe\x + 18.21.\x*.
\v 3 Neni ndichaisa chiso changu chichipikisa munhu uyo\x + 17.10.\x*, uye ndichamugura kubva pakati pevanhu vake, nokuti wakapa \add vamwe\add* vevana vake kuna Moreki\x + 20.5. Eki. 30.33.\x*, kuti asvibise imba yangu tsvene\x + Eze. 5.11; 23.38,39. Rev. 19.30.\x*, nekumhura zita rangu dzvene\x + 18.21.\x*.
\v 4 Zvino kana vanhu venyika vakatongoviga zviso zvavo kumunhu uyo kana achipa \add vamwe\add* vevana vake kuna Moreki, vakasamuuraya\x + Det. 17.2,3,5.\x*,
\v 5 ipapo ini ndichamisa chiso changu ndakapikisana nemunhu uyo nekupikisana nemhuri yake, ndigomugura\x + 20.5. Eki. 30.33.\x* nevose vanofeva shure kwake, kuti vaite ufeve vachitevera Moreki kubva pakati pevanhu vekwavo\x + Eki. 34.15.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Zvino mweya unotendeukira kune vane masvikiro nekuvavuki kuvatevera kuita upombwe\x + 19.31.\x*, ndichamisa chiso changu chichipikisana nemweya uyo\x + 17.10.\x*, uye ndichamugura kubva pavanhu vekwawo\x + 20.5. Eki. 30.33.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Naizvozvo zviitei vatsvene, mugova vatsvene; nokuti ndini Jehovha Mwari wenyu\x + 19.2; 11.44.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino muchachengeta zvimiso zvangu, nekuzviita\x + 18.4.\x*; ndini Jehovha anokuitai vatsvene\x + Eki. 31.13. Rev. 21.8,15,23; 22.2; Eze. 37.28.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Nokuti umwe neumwe anotuka baba vake kana mai vake achaurawa zvirokwazvo; anotuka baba vake kana mai vake\x + Eki. 21.17.\x*; ropa rake riri pamusoro pake\x + 20.11,12,13,16,27. 2 Zvak. 1.16. 1 Madz. 2.32,33,37.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Zvino munhu anoita upombwe nemukadzi wemunhu, nokuti anoita upombwe nemukadzi wewekwake, zvirokwazvo mhombwe nechifeve vachaurawa\x + 18.20. Det. 22.22. Joh. 8.4,5.\x*.
\v 11 Nemunhu anorara nemukadzi wababa vake, wafukura kushama kwababa vake; vese vari vaviri vachaurawa zvirokwazvo; ropa ravo richava pamusoro pavo\x + 18.8.\x*.
\v 12 Zvino murume, kana akarara nemukadzi wemwanakomana wake, vese vari vaviri vachaurawa zvirokwazvo\x + 18.15.\x*; vakaita zvinonyangadza\x + 18.23.\x*; ropa ravo richava pamusoro pavo.
\v 13 Zvino murume akarara nemunhurume \add se\add*kurara nemukadzi, vese vari vaviri vaita chinyangadzo; vachaurawa zvirokwazvo; ropa ravo richava pamusoro pavo\x + 18.22. Det. 23.17.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino munhu, kana akatora mukadzi pamwe namai vake, chinhu chakaipa; vachapiswa nemoto, iye naivo; kuti kurege kuva nechakaipa pakati penyu\x + 18.17. Det. 27.23.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino munhu, kana akarara nemhuka, achaurawa zvirokwazvo; uye muchauraya chipfuwo\x + 18.23. Det. 27.21.\x*.
\v 16 Zvino mukadzi, kana akaswedera kumhuka ipi neipi kuirarira, uchauraya mukadzi nemhuka; zvichaurawa zvirokwazvo; ropa razvo richava pamusoro pazvo.
\v 17 Zvino munhu, kana akatora hanzvadzi yake, mwanasikana wababa vake, kana mwanasikana wamai vake\x + 18.9. Det. 27.22.\x*, ndokuona kushama kwake, iyewo akaona kushama kwake, chinyadzo; vachagurwa pameso evana vevanhu vekwavo; wafukura kushama kwehanzvadzi yake; achatakura mhosva yake\x + Zvir. 14.34.\x*.
\v 18 Zvino murume, kana akarara nemukadzi murwere, akafukura kushama kwake\x + 18.19; 15.24.\x*, waona chitubu chake, naiye wafukura chitubu cheropa rake; zvino vaviri vavo vachagurwa kubva pakati pevanhu vekwavo\x + 12.7.\x*.
\v 19 Usafukura kushama kwemwanasikana wamai vamai vako, kana mwanasikana wamai vababa vako\x + 18.12,13.\x*; nokuti wafukura hama yako yepedo; vachatakura kuipa kwavo\x + 18.6.\x*.
\v 20 Zvino murume, kana akarara nemukadzi wababamunini vake, wafukura kushama kwababamunini vake; vachatakura chivi chavo; vachafa vasina vana\x + 18.14.\x*.
\v 21 Zvino murume, kana akatora mukadzi wemwana wamai vake, chinhu chisina kuchena; wafukura kushama kwemwana wamai vake; vachava vasina vana\x + 18.16.\x*.
\v 22 Naizvozvo chengetai zvimiso zvangu zvese, nemitongo yangu yose, nekuzviita\x + 18.4.\x*, kuti nyika kwandinokuisai kugara mairi irege kukurutsai\x + 18.25,28.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Zvino musafamba netsika dzerudzi rwandichadzinga pamberi penyu\x + 18.3.\x*; nokuti vakaita izvozvo zvese, naizvozvo ndakavasema\x + 18.27. Det. 9.5.\x*.
\v 24 Asi ndati kwamuri: Imi muchagara nhaka yenyika yavo, ini ndigoipa kwamuri kuigara nhaka\x + Eki. 3.17; 6.8.\x*, nyika inoyerera mukaka neuchi; ndini Jehovha Mwari wenyu\x + Eki. 3.8.\x*, wakakutsaurai kubva pandudzi\x + 20.26. 1 Madz. 8.53; Eki. 19.5; 33.16.\x*.
\v 25 Naizvozvo isai mutsauko pakati pemhuka dzakachena nedzisina kuchena, uye pakati peshiri dzakachena nedzisina kuchena\x + 11.2-47; Det. 14.4-20.\x*; kuti murege kuita mweya yenyu inonyangadza nemhuka kana neshiri kana nechipi nechipi chinokambaira pavhu chandakatsaura kwamuri sechisina kuchena\x + 11.43.\x*.
\v 26 Zvino muchava vatsvene kwandiri, nokuti ini Jehovha ndiri mutsvene\x + 20.7;11.44.\x*, uye ndakakutsaurai kubva pandudzi, kuti muve vangu\x + 20.24.\x*.
\p
\v 27 Uye murume kana mukadzi, kana vane svikiro mavari, kana muvuki, vachaurawa zvirokwazvo\x + 19.31.\x*; vachavataka nemabwe\x + 20.2.\x*; ropa ravo richava pamusoro pavo\x + 20.9.\x*.